<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Otto Eyring</head><p>Der Rat teilt wegen Eyrings verstorbenen Schwagers Wenzel Pfinzing mit, dass die beiden Vormunde Anton Derrer und Konrad II. Haller, Bürger zu Nürnberg, entsprechend dem beurkundeten Testament verfahren sind, und verweist auf den Rechtsweg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_534" id="266v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_534_r1l19">Otten Eyring / Rat v̈ber </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_534_r1l20"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Eÿrıng / Als du vns <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> haſt von vvencʒla </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_534_r1l22">Pfincʒings 
<del rend="strikethrough">des </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_534_r1l21"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> </ab></add> deins Swagers <expan>ſelige<ex>n</ex></expan> geſcheffts wegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_534_r1l23">Darümb <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir dıe vormund <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geſcheffts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_534_r1l24"><expan>mitname<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Anth<ex>oni</ex></expan> <expan>derr<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Cuncʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> haller <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_534_r1l25">beſant vnd cʒu rede geſacʒt / vnd dıe <expan>ſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Er hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_534_r1l26">ſeins geſcheffts wol macht gehabt / als ſıe das mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_534_r1l27"><expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>beſigelte<ex>n</ex></expan> brief wol <expan>bringe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> / deuht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_534_r1l28">dich aber daʒ du darüber cʒu den <expan>vormund<ex>en</ex></expan> ıcht cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_534_r1l29"><expan>ſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> heteſt / <expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir dir von Jn <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_534_r1l30">ſlewnigs <expan>reht<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vven<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir des <expan>erma<ex>n</ex>t</expan> <expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan> ſo <expan>dieſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_534_r1l32"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>anh<ex>eim</ex></expan> ſind / vnd <expan>vven<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> alſo </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_534_r1l31">du darumb </ab></add> ın den nehſten vıer <expan>woch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_535" id="267r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_535_r1l2">
<del rend="strikethrough">darümb </del> her cʒu vns kümſt / So ſoltu <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> geleite <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_535_r1l3">
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒu vns </del> bey vns vnd von vns für vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_535_r1l4">ongeuerde / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_534" id="266v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Otten Eyring, rat über </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Eyring, als du uns
                                                  <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hast von
                                                Wenczla Pfinczings,
                                                  <add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan></add>, deins
                                                swagers, <expan>selige<ex>n,</ex></expan> gescheffts
                                                wegen, darümb <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir die
                                                vormund <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                                                gescheffts, <expan>mitname<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Anth<ex>oni</ex></expan>
<expan>Derr<ex>er</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>Cuncze<ex>n</ex></expan> Haller,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, besant und czu rede
                                                gesaczt; und die <expan>sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                                er hab seins gescheffts wol macht gehabt, als sie
                                                das mit <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>besigelte<ex>n</ex></expan> brief wol
                                                  <expan>bringe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n.</ex></expan> Deuht dich aber, daz
                                                du darüber czu den <expan>vormund<ex>en</ex></expan>
                                                icht czu <expan>sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hetest,
                                                  <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir dir von in
                                                  <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan>
                                                slewnigs <expan>reht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> wir des
                                                  <expan>erma<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan>, so
                                                  <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>anh<ex>eim</ex></expan> sind; und
                                                  <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>du darumb</add> in den nehsten vier
                                                  <expan>woch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<pb facs="#facs_535" id="267r"/> her czu uns kümst, so sol tu
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> geleite
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> bey uns und von uns,
                                                für uns und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on
                                                geverde. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>sup<ex>ra.</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
